message.body: Hello! How's your Friday night going?
Good. Just decorated my window
Aww you're getting Christmas-ed up!! I haven't done that in years!!! How's it looking?
Good. I just sent a picture. Don't know if you'll get it. It's all peanut themed. We have Charlie Brown, snoopy, Woodstock, and Linus along with the Charlie Brown christmas tree.
That's adorable! Yea, my phone hasn't been receiving or sending picture messages :( I'm happy that you're even getting my text at all hahah.
Indeed! But now I'm so exhausted. Haha. But how's your Friday?
Not much going on. I was thinking how we haven't seen each other for such a ridiculous amount of time. How come we didn't go out today??
Not sure. But I don't think I would have anyway. I helped put up the decorations. But I'm sure Sammy didn't want to go out and Edens working night shift tonight.
I believe.
Ohhhh. Yea I didn't get the text from Sam. I saw her post on FB. That's terrible.
I know. So sad. So I figured she'd rather stay with her brother.
It's been a rough couple of months for her. I feel bad.
Me too.
Any plans for the weekend?
Not really. I might go to the mall tomorrow to do some more shopping. You?
Just work and home. Wow, you're really in the shopping mood aren't you? Hagah, good to be the people on your Christmas list!
Haha. It's just my mom and dad.
I guess you're done shopping for Seyer?
Yeah. I bought him some shirts and a wallet.
You're an early bird!!! Makes me feel like I'm so behind.
Haha. I did Black Friday shopping. Don't feel bad.
I need to start moving! Do you want to go get breakfast this Sunday?
Oh yeah sure! That'd be fun!
I'm planning to go with Sam to Sabrina's, or Green Eggs, or Cafe Lift, or some place, some place like that!
Awesome!!!
Any preferences???
I say green eggs or Sabrina's. I don't think I liked cafe lift too much.
Okay! Good, I'm glad you're narrowing down the options hahah! Want to say 11?
Sounds great! But I'm starting to doze off so I'm gonna get some sleep. But keep me posted :)
Sure thing! Night!!!
Hey. So if we go out tomorrow, can we push it back a little? Like 12 instead of 11?
Sure! I'm good with that.
Do you think we'll be done by 3?
I think we should be. I don't think it'll take us three hours to eat. I know I eat slow but that would be ridiculous (even for me) hahah!
Okay. Cause my mom wants to go to the mall and I dont wanna make her wait, you know?
Yea, no problemo!
Okay. Is Sammy still going and where are we goings
*going?
